521
00:31:21,180 --> 00:31:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] Smetalo me jako, ali sad sam svi okej s mojim nosom.

522
00:31:24,039 --> 00:31:26,339
[SPEAKER_01] Šta smo mi priđali?

523
00:31:26,339 --> 00:31:28,180
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto je bilo ozbiljno, čini mi se.

524
00:31:28,180 --> 00:31:29,500
